---
title: Steakhouse-Style Bison Patties with Creamy Mushroom Gravy and Chive Mash
description: Hearty, lean bison pairs perfectly with bold and rich flavours like this delicious mushroom gravy! We've dialed up the elegance with tender broccolini and buttery chive mash.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/steakhouse-style-bison-patties-ac4cb638.jpg
